nyone who asks for an invitation. When there is no room for more guests the host can log in to <a href="http://petitesplanetes.cc/">petitesplanetes.cc</a> and change the status of the screening to fully booked.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I will help spread the word about the private-public screenings via Twitter and Facebook. And you are of course encouraged to announce your event and spread the word via your social networks and personal websites if possible.</p>\r\n</div>', 'Host a Screening', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '40-revision-12', '', '', '2011-10-18 20:28:47', '2011-10-18 20:28:47', '', 40, 'http://localhost:8888/lulacruza/40-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
